#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/apache.rst:2
msgid "Apache"
msgstr "Apache"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/apache.rst:5
msgid "后缀解析"
msgstr "Extension Parsing"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/apache.rst:6
msgid ""
"``test.php.x1.x2.x3`` （ x1,x2,x3 为没有在 mime.types 文件中定义的文件类型）。Apache "
"将从右往左开始判断后缀， 若x3为非可识别后缀，则判断x2，直到找到可识别后缀为止，然后对可识别后缀进行解析"
msgstr ""
"``test.php.x1.x2.x3`` where ``x1``, ``x2``, and ``x3`` are file types not "
"defined in ``mime.types``. Apache checks extensions from right to left. If "
"``x3`` is not recognized, it checks ``x2`` until a recognized extension is "
"found, then parses the file according to that extension."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/apache.rst:9
msgid ".htaccess"
msgstr ".htaccess"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/apache.rst:10
msgid "当AllowOverride被启用时，上传启用解析规则的.htaccess"
msgstr ""
"When ``AllowOverride`` is enabled, upload an ``.htaccess`` file that enables"
" parsing rules."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/apache.rst:40
msgid "目录遍历"
msgstr "Directory Listing"

